SIMPHIWE NGUBANE AMAPHOYISA aphenya icala lokudutshulwa kubulawe owesilisa (31) obekade edayisa utshwala ongenelwe ngabantu kubo Osindisweni, ngaseVerulam, entathakusa yangoLwesibili. Okhulumela amaphoyisa KwaZulu-Natal, uColonel Thembeka Mbele, uthe kuvulwe icala lokubulala eliphenywa ngamaphoyisa asesiteshini saseVerulam. Uthe umufi udutshulwe ekhanda washonela endaweni yesehlakalo. Abezimo eziphuthumayo enkampanini yonogada, iReaction Unit South Africa (Rusa), badalule ukuthi bafike kulo muzi ababebizelwe khona, bafica umufi edindilize kusofa. Okhulumela iRusa, uMnuz Prem Balram, uthe kuthe uma exilongwa emzimbeni umufi obenejoyinti, kwatholakala amanxeba okudutshulwa ekhanda nasesifubeni. UBalram uthe babikelwe wumfowabo kamufi ukuthi obulewe wayekade esegunjini lakhe lokulala ngesikhathi amadoda amathathu abehlomile engena ngewindi. Kuthiwa amadoda amabili kulawa amathathu alalise phansi ngezisu abebesendlini. Kuvela ukuthi la madoda abe esehamba ngephaseji ebheke egunjini lokulala likamufi afika emnyango amemeza, emyalela ukuba awuvule. “Kuthiwa avele asikhahlela isicabha angena ngaphakathi egunjini. Kuqale ngokuthi kube nokuhilizisana phakathi kwamadoda nomufi okuphethe ngokuthi adutshulwe. La madoda abe esethatha kwasani ethathekayo endlini, kubalwa utshwala nesamba semali esingadalulwanga, abaleka ngemoto,” kusho uBalram. 